a Regia con El Dorado\n |OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2017|3|15}}\n | AltDate = June 7, 2017\n |Viewers = 1.64<ref>{{cite web|last1=Pucci|first1=Douglas|title=Wednesday Final Nationals: Warriors-Cavaliers on ABC Posts 19-Year High in NBA Finals Game 3 Total Viewership|url=http://programminginsider.com/ratings/final-nationals/wednesday-final-nationals-warriors-cavaliers-abc-posts-19-year-high-nba-finals-game-3-total-viewership/|website=programminginsider.com|accessdate=8 June 2017}}</ref>\n |ShortSummary = Danilo takes Estela with El Dorado so that she interprets her songs and puts herself to his service. From now on, Regia belongs to him.\n |LineColor = 12234E\n}}\n{{Episode list\n |EpisodeNumber =  24\n |Title = Ryan quiere proteger a Paloma\n |OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2017|3|16}}\n | AltDate = June 8, 2017\n |Viewers = 1.75<ref>{{cite web|last1=Pucci|first1=Douglas|title=Thursday Final Nationals: Nearly 20 Million Tune In to James Comey Testimony Across Various Networks|url=http://programminginsider.com/ratings/final-nationals/thursday-final-nationals-nearly-20-million-tune-james-comey-testimony-across-various-networks/|website=programminginsider.com|accessdate=10 June 2017}}</ref>\n |ShortSummary = Ryan asks Estela to give him custody of Paloma, since Danilo is in danger.\n |LineColor = 12234E\n}}\n{{Episode list\n |EpisodeNumber =  25\n |Title = Furia Productions lanza a Morgana como solista\n |OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2017|3|17}}\n | AltDate = June 9, 2017\n |Viewers = 1.51<ref>{{cite web|last1=Pucci|first1=Douglas|title=Friday Final Nationals: ABC Earns 14-Year Friday Best in Adults 18-49 Delivery with Warriors-Cavaliers NBA Finals Game 4|url=http://programminginsider.com/ratings/final-nationals/friday-final-nationals-warriors-cavaliers-abc-delivers-second-best-nba-finals-game-4-viewership-13-years/|website=programminginsider.com|accessdate=12 June 2017}}</ref>\n |ShortSummary = Danilo gives Morgana a chance to release an album as a soloist. Ryan