mer-Bests|url=http://programminginsider.com/ratings/final-nationals/tuesday-final-nationals-msnbc-prime-time-shows-achieve-summer-bests/|website=programminginsider.com|accessdate=24 September 2017}}</ref>\n |ShortSummary = Estela gives a gun to Asdr\u00fabal so he can use it against Danilo. What he never imagined was that he would be betrayed, since the weapon was defective and Danilo took advantage to finish his life.\n |LineColor = 12234E\n}}\n{{Episode list\n |EpisodeNumber =  70\n |Title = Ryan descubre las mentiras de Estela\n |OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2017|5|19}}\n | AltDate = August 16, 2017\n |Viewers = 1.60<ref>{{cite web|last1=Pucci|first1=Douglas|title=Wednesday Final Nationals: \u2018Marlon\u2019 on NBC Tops Summer Scripted Debuts Among Young Adults|url=http://programminginsider.com/ratings/final-nationals/wednesday-final-nationals-marlon-nbc-tops-summer-scripted-debuts-among-young-adults/|website=programminginsider.com|accessdate=24 September 2017}}</ref>\n |ShortSummary = Ryan faces Estela to tell her that all this time he faked affection and stayed by her side to find out if she really had a double life.\n |LineColor = 12234E\n}}\n{{Episode list\n |EpisodeNumber =  71<hr />72\n |Title = Gran final\n |OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2017|5|21}}\n | AltDate = August 17, 2017<hr />August 18, 2017\n |Viewers = 1.67<ref>{{cite web|last1=Pucci|first1=Douglas|title=Thursday Final Nationals: With NFL Preseason Football, ESPN Beats ABC and Fox in Prime Time|url=http://programminginsider.com/ratings/final-nationals/thursday-final-nationals-nfl-preseason-football-espn-beats-abc-fox-prime-time/|website=programminginsider.com|accessdate=1 September 2017}}</ref><hr />1.93<ref>{{cite web|last1=Pucci|first1=Douglas|title=Friday Final Nationals: \u2018Big Brother 19\u2019 Recap Special on CBS Tops Prime Time|url=http://programminginsider.com/ratings/final-nationals/friday-final-nationals-big-brother-19-recap-special-cbs-tops-prime-time/|website=programminginsider