a de \"El dorado\"\n |OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2017|2|15}}\n |ShortSummary    = El Calao has all the details about the festival of El Dorado, where Los Jerarcas de la Sierra de Danilo Cabrera were to set the mood.\n |LineColor       =898FFD\n}}\n{{Episode list\n |EpisodeNumber   = 5\n |Title           = Apareci\u00f3 la verdadera Estela Carrillo\n |OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2017|5|8}}\n |ShortSummary    = Steve narrates the experience that lived Ryan and Laura, when finding the true Estela Carrillo.\n |LineColor       = 898FFD\n}}\n}}\n\n===''Cocina de Chayo'' (2017)===\n{{Episode table\n|background  = #F57466\n|total_width = 90\n|overall     = 11\n|title       = 58\n|airdate     = 13\n|aux4        = 8\n|aux4T       = Length<br />(minutes)\n{{Episode list\n |EpisodeNumber   = 1\n |Title           = Receta de Cachapas\n |OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2017|2|16}}\n |ShortSummary    = In the kitchen of Chayo we present you a simple but delicious recipe. The cachapa is one of the star dishes of Venezuelan and Colombian food.\n |Aux4            = 1:22\n |LineColor       = F57466\n}}\n{{Episode list\n |EpisodeNumber   = 2\n |Title           = Panqueques con dulce de leche\n |OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2017|3|2}}\n |Aux4            = 01:02\n |ShortSummary    = Chayo teaches you to prepare pancakes with dulce de leche.\n |LineColor       = F57466\n}}\n{{Episode list\n |EpisodeNumber   = 3\n |Title           = Pasta a la mexicana\n |OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2017|3|15}}\n |Aux4            = 1:16\n |ShortSummary    = Chayo teaches you how to prepare Mexican pasta.\n |LineColor       = F57466\n}}\n{{Episode list\n |EpisodeNumber   = 4\n |Title           = Tapitas de camar\u00f3n\n |OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2017|3|22}}\n |Aux4            = 1:49\n |ShortSummary    = Chayo teaches you how to prepare tapitas de camar\u00f3n.\n |LineColor       = F57466\n}}\n{{Episode list\n |EpisodeNumber   = 5\n |Title           = Pizza de sand\u00eda\n |OriginalAirDate